1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 15=

4
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,200
Qin Yu.

5
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,360
Do you smell it?

6
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,760
This is the mugwort scent I know best.

7
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,000
Whenever I smell it,

8
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:07,760
I feel at ease.

9
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:09,680
It makes me feel like
there's hope for the future.

10
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:22,320
Then,

11
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,280
is there a place for me

12
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,440
in your future?

13
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:40,080
Xiaoduo.

14
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:40,680
I...

15
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,280
Don't get me wrong.

16
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:41,920
I wasn't...

17
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:43,640
That's not what I meant.

18
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,640
Let me mark you.

19
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:48,040
That way, you'll be mine alone.

20
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,400
Really?

21
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,120
Xiaoduo.

22
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,520
What?

23
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:56,480
Does it really hurt that much?

24
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,440
No, it doesn't hurt.

25
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:58,720
Go ahead and do it.

26
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,480
I'll let you.

27
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,160
Really, go ahead.

28
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,040
You goof.

29
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:04,960
By the way, Xiaoduo.

30
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:07,040
Wait here for me.

31
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:07,920
I'll be right back.

32
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,440
Where are you going?

33
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:11,880
It's a surprise.

34
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,120
Wait for me to come back.

35
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,000
Wait for me, Xiaoduo.

36
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:21,840
Xiaoduo!

37
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,720
No!

38
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:25,640
Xiaoduo.

39
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:26,280
Qin Yu.

40
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:26,920
No!

41
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,320
Qin Yu.

42
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:29,960
Qin Yu.

43
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,680
No!

44
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,920
Wake up, Qin Yu.

45
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,480
Who were you talking to just now?

46
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,080
What did I just say?

47
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,240
Answer my question first.

48
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:46,080
Who were you talking to just now?

49
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:52,720
Weren't you talking to Qiao Xiaomi?

50
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,320
You're getting a little too nosy.

51
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,200
I'm telling you.

52
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,520
No matter what I said,

53
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,680
you can't tell anyone.

54
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,400
What secret are you hiding?

55
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,440
I don't have any secrets.

56
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,600
There you are, my MVP.

57
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:36,720
Come on.

58
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,280
Sit down.

59
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,320
I'm in a great mood today.

60
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,320
Zhiwei.

61
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,960
You got the news pretty fast.

62
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,840
Now you've got

63
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,800
the gallery in your hands too.

64
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,480
Hurry up and get married.

65
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,440
Come.

66
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,920
Let's celebrate in advance.

67
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,800
If we're celebrating,
let's do it properly.

68
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:18,280
That's the thing your subconscious
cares about most.

69
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,480
Maybe it's also what
you most want to forget.

70
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,160
Why did you come to me? Say something.

71
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,200
If you won't talk, I'm leaving.

72
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,000
I'm really leaving.

73
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,880
Don't do anything stupid.

74
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:07,988
♪The bud is tinted into wisdom♪

75
00:05:07,988 --> 00:05:11,760
♪Raising butterflies♪

76
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:14,460
♪Strong and radiant♪

77
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:20,200
♪Adorning the lilies♪

78
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:24,680
♪Weaving together clouds and poetry♪

79
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:31,427
♪Circling at the edge of sunset♪

80
00:05:31,935 --> 00:05:36,528
♪Come walk along my secret path,
my diamond-like heart♪

81
00:05:36,553 --> 00:05:40,040
♪From the ruins rise dazzling thorns♪

82
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:44,120
♪The footprints of angels and beasts♪

83
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:47,600
♪They are all a part of me♪

84
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:51,360
♪Watering these vines
to the ends of the earth♪

85
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:54,880
♪I am so heavy, yet so rich♪

86
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:59,280
♪Great disasters, ordinary joys♪

87
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:02,400
♪Let them drift away with the wind♪

88
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:08,680
♪In exchange for
the richness of my soil♪

89
00:06:53,566 --> 00:06:58,280
♪Tempering my cold eyes,
scorching my back♪

90
00:06:58,280 --> 00:07:01,640
♪Cast into the ashes,
evolving into islands♪

91
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:05,230
♪In the end,
I become the one who can weave♪

92
00:07:06,023 --> 00:07:08,900
♪Rivers that wind around♪

93
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:13,240
♪Watering these vines
to the ends of the earth♪

94
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:16,840
♪So heavy, yet so rich♪

95
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:21,081
♪Great disasters, ordinary joys♪

96
00:07:21,081 --> 00:07:24,480
♪Let them drift away with the wind♪

97
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:27,280
♪In exchange for♪

98
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:32,060
♪The richness of my soil♪

99
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,200
(What am I doing?)

100
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,840
(Xiaomi.)

101
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,520
(Something came up at the gallery,
so I have to go.)

102
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,160
(Don't forget to eat breakfast.)

103
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,840
(After what happened last night,)

104
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,560
(he just left this morning.)

105
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:05,160
(He left me here all by myself.)

106
00:10:06,739 --> 00:10:08,809
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

107
00:10:08,809 --> 00:10:12,229
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

108
00:10:13,829 --> 00:10:15,719
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

109
00:10:15,719 --> 00:10:19,709
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

110
00:10:20,949 --> 00:10:22,809
♪Let me go, set me free♪

111
00:10:22,809 --> 00:10:26,849
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

112
00:10:27,389 --> 00:10:32,799
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

113
00:10:34,149 --> 00:10:36,289
♪The freedom you gave me♪

114
00:10:36,289 --> 00:10:39,929
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

115
00:10:41,189 --> 00:10:43,459
♪Love can barely move forward♪

116
00:10:43,459 --> 00:10:47,239
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

117
00:10:48,339 --> 00:10:50,579
♪The closeness I long for♪

118
00:10:50,579 --> 00:10:54,969
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

119
00:10:55,379 --> 00:10:57,199
♪I don't want to break free♪

120
00:10:57,199 --> 00:11:02,569
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
